<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #e1e4e8;
        border-radius: 12px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .logo {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #6366f1;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #6366f1;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 40px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <a href="#" class="logo">OneVault</a>
      </div>
      <h2>Family Invitation</h2>
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p><strong>{{inviterName}}</strong>
        has invited you to join their family vault on OneVault.</p>
      <p>By joining, you can securely share passwords, bank details, and
        important documents with each other.</p>

      <p>To accept this invitation and set up your account, click the button
        below:</p>

      <a href="{{inviteUrl}}" class="btn">Join Family Vault</a>

      <p>If you already have an account, you can accept the invitation from the
        "Family" section in your dashboard.</p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>If you weren't expecting this invitation, you can safely ignore this
          email.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2026 OneVault. Securely protecting what matters most.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>